What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Kids Travel Bags Market?

Market Analysis and Insights

Kids Travel Bags Market

The kids travel bags market is expected to be growing at a growth rate of 9.60% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Data Bridge Market Research analyses the factors responsible for fostering the growth of kids travel bags market. This rise in kids travel bags market value can be attributed to the various factors such as increased focus of the product manufacturers on product innovations, surging educational tours for the students, growing popularity of e-commerce platforms especially in the developing economies and increasing personal disposable income.

From the name itself, it is clear that the kids travel bags are the bags that are specifically designed to be carried for travelling purposes. Like any other bag, the kids travel bags provide sufficient space for packaging all the necessary items such as clothes, toiletries, snack items and much more. The kids travel bags are available in a wide range of shapes and sizes and can be availed via both online and offline modes of distribution.

Growth and expansion of travel and tourism industry and increasing personal disposable income are the major factors fostering the growth of the kids travel bags market. Growing fondness for adventure sports and trekking among the youngsters, growth in the demand for personal luggage by children, rise in the research and development activities and rising globalization and westernization are some other indirect kids travel bags market growth determinants. Growing penetration of e-commerce platforms, rising availability of ultra-lightweight trolley bags, rising demand for trendy and fashionable kids trolley bags, surging availability of better manufacturing machines for travel bags and growing awareness about the popular brands will also create lucrative and remunerative kids travel bags market growth opportunities in the long run.

On the flip side, availability of low quality counterfeit products will pose a major challenge to the growth of kids travel bags market in the long run. Fluctuations in the prices of raw materials will further derail the kids travel bags market growth rate. Intense pricing pressure among the vendors and difficulty in organising all the time will yet again hamper the kids travel bags market growth rate.

